Acknowledgements

Awesome things happen because of awesome people. Here is a page to recognize some amazing efforts.

  • SkiteInnit : Inspiration, rallying the troops, serious staying power. We would not be talking about any of this without Skite. He’s got us all back on the horse, and every new piece of content he puts out is like the bat signal. He’s ambitious, relentless, and passionate on another level. But in my opinion his best trait is his honesty and integrity. I have a lot of respect for him.
  • junedgasp : This guy does everything, not sure what else to say other than he deserves his flowers. He dives so deep on cryptanalysis, he’s become nothing short of an expert in a litle over a year. Going from throwing things together in spreadsheets to generating his own tools and collaborating with other great talent, and teaching others. Resilience and persistence define him. Hats off.
